  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "前言",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300028060_4_1617-1808",
          "range": "1617-1808",
          "rangeStart": 1617,
          "rangeEnd": 1808,
          "markText": "需要指出的是，阻碍民主实现的各种因素构成极为复杂，我们很难完全揭示以及精准阐述。尽管如此，我们仍可以作出归纳，其决定因素有以下三个：（1）人的天性；（2）政治斗争的性质；（3）组织属性。笔者的核心观点是“民主会导致寡头政治，因其本身包含某种寡头政治的因素”。这并不意味着笔者要对任何政党、政府以及个人进行道德层面上的谴责，而是客观阐述所有组织内在包含的一种社会学规律，并无好坏之分。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1747618648,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-19 09:37:28",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1617&rangeEnd=1808",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1617&rangeEnd=1808"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "chapterTitle": "第六章 综论：组织的寡头化倾向",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300028060_11_31222-31283",
          "range": "31222-31283",
          "rangeStart": 31222,
          "rangeEnd": 31283,
          "markText": "各种各样的民主体制都会发展出寡头政治，这是所有组织发展的趋势。也就是说，无论是社会主义组织还是自由主义组织都存在这个趋势。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1747618619,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-19 09:36:59",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=31222&rangeEnd=31283",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=31222&rangeEnd=31283"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "总序",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300028060_3_583-649",
          "range": "583-649",
          "rangeStart": 583,
          "rangeEnd": 649,
          "markText": "近代政治就是政党政治。国家权力主要由政党掌握，并且通过政党运行。如果说主权国家是国际政治舞台的主角，那么政党便是国内政治舞台的主角。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714568869,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-01 21:07:49",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=583&rangeEnd=649",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=583&rangeEnd=649"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_19598-19646",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "19598-19646",
      "markText": "社会主义领导人存在的这种倾向并不是一种偶然，这源于社会主义政党与军事组织在理念上存在某种亲和力。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19598&rangeEnd=19646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19598&rangeEnd=19646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_43026-43086",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "43026-43086",
      "markText": "大众有着强烈的个人崇拜渴望，他们朴素的唯心主义需要世俗神灵来填补。他们对这个世俗神灵的崇拜越盲目，就越能应付艰苦的生活。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=43026&rangeEnd=43086",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=43026&rangeEnd=43086"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_5_951-984",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "951-984",
      "markText": "从法律层面讲，君主政体只能被上帝废除，但上帝的意志又是不可探知的。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=951&rangeEnd=984",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=951&rangeEnd=984"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_5_11828-11903",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11828-11903",
      "markText": "那些资产阶级的新贵们急切地融入贵族阶层以求获得旧的统治阶层对他们的认可，即赋予他们与旧的统治阶级作为同一阶层的合法性资格，除此之外，再也没有其他追求。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11828&rangeEnd=11903",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11828&rangeEnd=11903"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_3278-3347",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3278-3347",
      "markText": "法律通过各种灵活的形式讨论产生。在讨论中，由主席首先公布主要议题并开始讨论，接着讨论次要议题，最后就结果进行投票，得票最多的草案获得通过。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3278&rangeEnd=3347",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3278&rangeEnd=3347"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_4_2204-2275",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2204-2275",
      "markText": "政党生发于个体的利益与情感，其内部组织结构和目标等许多方面表现得与国家极为相似，因此它也可以被称为一个“个人国家”，或者说是一个“国中之国”。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2204&rangeEnd=2275",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2204&rangeEnd=2275"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_7_84720-84795",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "84720-84795",
      "markText": "近年来，尤其是民主国家的统治阶层希望通过向工人阶级杰出领导人开放政府职位来压制愈演愈烈的工人革命运动，这其实就是试图通过分享极为有限的权力来驯服革命。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=84720&rangeEnd=84795",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=84720&rangeEnd=84795"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_5_10031-10079",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10031-10079",
      "markText": "熟悉历史的人都不难发现，任何获得统治地位的阶级都会极力思考，如何将他们积累的政治权力传给下一代。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10031&rangeEnd=10079",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10031&rangeEnd=10079"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_27098-27163",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "27098-27163",
      "markText": "只要选举义务没有取代选举权利，少数人就总有可能获得多数人自愿放弃的权利，进而利用这种权利强迫政治冷漠的大多数人接受他们制定的法律。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=27098&rangeEnd=27163",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=27098&rangeEnd=27163"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_7_54999-55017",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "54999-55017",
      "markText": "“人总是被他创造出来的东西所控制”。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=54999&rangeEnd=55017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=54999&rangeEnd=55017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_23657-23699",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "23657-23699",
      "markText": "在此基础上，小仲马进一步指出，平庸的多数只能代表现在，积极创新的少数则往往代表着未来",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300028060&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=23657&rangeEnd=23699",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d2232790813ab7176g01065c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=23657&rangeEnd=23699"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300028060_6_55364-55434",
